<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- أَوْ رَكْعَةً مُنْفَرِدًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَمْ تَصِحَّ صَلَاتُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَإِذَا جَمَعَهُمَا مَسْجِدٌ؛ صَحَّتِ القُدْوَةُ مُطْلَقًا،<span style="color:#006d98"> بِشَرْطِ:</span> العِلْمِ بِانْتِقَالَاتِ الإِمَامِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ لَمْ يَجْمَعْهُمَا شُرِطَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- رُؤْيَةُ الإِمَامِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- أَوْ مَنْ وَرَاءَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلَوْ فِي بَعْضِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَكُرِهَ عُلُوُّ إِمَامٍ عَلَى مَأْمُومٍ ذِرَاعًا فَأَكْثَرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- لَا عَكْسُهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَكُرِهَ حُضُورُ مَسْجِدٍ، وَجَمَاعَةٍ لِمَنْ أَكَلَ بَصَلًا أَوْ فُجْلًا وَنَحْوَهُ حَتَّى يَذْهَبَ رِيحُهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> يُعْذَرُ بِتَرْكِ جُمُعَةٍ وَجَمَاعَةٍ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> <span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> مَرِيضٌ، وَخَائِفٌ حُدُوثَ مَرَضٍ لَيْسَا بِالمَسْجِدِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَمَنْ يُدَافِعُ أَحَدَ الأَخْبَثَيْنِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>